text: Achachi Qala (Aymara for "gigantic stone", Hispanicized spelling Achachicala) is a mountain in the Bolivian Andes. It is located in the La Paz Department, Murillo Province, Palca Municipality. Achachi Qala lies southwest of Ch'iyar Qullu. == References == Category:Mountains of La Paz Department (Bolivia)
title: Achachi Qala (Murillo)
